text: "Mysterious Times" is a 1998 dance and trance song by the German DJ group Sash! and featured English singer Tina Cousins. It is the second single from Sash!'s second studio album Life Goes On which was released on 17 August 1998. ==Charts== ===Weekly charts=== Chart (1998–2000) Peak position Australia (ARIA) 62 Denmark (IFPI) 6 Europe (Eurochart Hot 100) 6 Iceland (Íslenski Listinn Topp 40) 22 Italy (Musica e dischi) 5 US Dance Club Play (Billboard) 11 ===Year-end charts=== Chart (1998) Position Belgium (Ultratop 50 Flanders) 96 Belgium (Ultratop 50 Wallonia) 80 Europe (Eurochart Hot 100) 54 France (SNEP) 85 Sweden (Sverigetopplistan) 93 UK Singles (OCC) 47 ==Certifications== ==References== ==Other websites== *Mysterious Times on YouTube Category:1998 songs Category:Sash! songs
